  ('AGENESIS OF DORSAL PANCREAS','agenesis_of_dorsal_pancreas','AND SPLENIC DISORDERS','','short round pancreatic head adjacent to duodenum','','{}','{"short round pancreatic head adjacent to duodenum","absence of pancreatic neck, body, tail, duct of Santorini, minor duodenal papilla"}','{"general": ["short round pancreatic head adjacent to duodenum", "absence of pancreatic neck, body, tail, duct of Santorini, minor duodenal papilla"]}','{}','processed_clusters/disease_entries/and_splenic_disorders/agenesis_of_dorsal_pancreas.md'),
